trans-unit.source: Specifies the name of a cryptographic hash algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Angir navnet på en kryptografisk nummeralgoritme.

trans-unit.source: The HashAlgorithmName structure includes some static properties that return predefined hash algorithm names, as well as a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name%2A> property that can represent a custom hash algorithm name as a strongly-typed string.
trans-unit.target: Strukturen HashAlgorithmName inneholder noen statiske egenskaper som returnerer forhåndsdefinerte hash algoritmen navn, i tillegg til en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name%2A>egenskapen som kan representere et egendefinert hash-algoritmenavn som en strongly-typed-streng.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.HashAlgorithmName.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: Hash algorithm names are case-sensitive.
trans-unit.target: Det skilles hash-algoritmen navn.

trans-unit.source: Asymmetric algorithms implemented using Microsoft's CNG (Cryptographic Next Generation) API interpret the underlying string value as a [CNG algorithm identifier](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/aa375534.aspx).
trans-unit.target: Algoritmer for asymmetriske implementeres ved hjelp av Microsofts CNG (kryptografisk neste generasjon) API tolke underliggende strengverdien som en [algoritme-ID for CNG](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/aa375534.aspx).

trans-unit.source: Asymmetric algorithms implemented using other technologies: - Must recognize at least "MD5", "SHA1", "SHA256", "SHA384", and "SHA512".
trans-unit.target: Algoritmer for asymmetriske implementeres ved hjelp av andre teknologier:-må gjenkjenne minst "MD5", "SHA1", "SHA256", "SHA384" og "SHA512".

trans-unit.source: - Should recognize additional CNG identifiers for any additional hash algorithms that they support.
trans-unit.target: -Skal gjenkjenne flere CNG-identifikatorer for flere hashalgoritmer de støtter.
